song.title: Disco Del Copstation
song.info:
"I remember I was pleased with the tune when I released it. Now I somehow feel its not disco enough. Oh, and Nico delivered it to the compo, that's why the results say Reed and Nico."
Ranked 8th in the tracked music compo at Mekka & Symposium 2002 held in Heidmarkhalle, Fallingbostel, Germany from 29th March to 1st April, 2002.
Ranked 3rd in the multichannel music compo at TRSAC FU held in Copenhagen, Denmark from 15th to 18th August, 2002.
